Thought I told you
to leave your father at home.

14:37.080 --> 14:38.520
[in Norwegian]
That isn't funny, Johnny.

14:38.600 --> 14:40.600
[urine trickling]

14:42.200 --> 14:43.960
[in Norwegian]
What kind of ward have they put you in?

